<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-accent-50 section-padding">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <a
          href="https://www.cop-cv.org/ventanilla-unica/busqueda-de-psicologos/psicologo/CV18378"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6 cursor-pointer"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Psicóloga Colegiada CV-18378
          </div>
        </a>

        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
          Soy <span class="text-primary-600">Aitana Escrivà Conde</span>,
          psicóloga en Castellón
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Te ayudo a superar tus dificultades emocionales con un enfoque humano
          y profesional.<br />
          <strong
            >Especializada en ansiedad, depresión, problemas de pareja y trauma.</strong
          ><br /><br />
          Ofrezco un enfoque personalizado y basado en la <strong
            >evidencia científica</strong
          > para tu bienestar emocional y <strong>físico</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-8">
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/34691804629?text=Hola%20Aitana,%20me%20gustaría%20información%20sobre%20tus%20servicios%20de%20psicología"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-primary text-center"
          >
            Contactar por WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a href="/servicios" class="btn-secondary text-center">
            Ver Servicios
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center space-x-6 text-sm text-neutral-600">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>+1.000 pacientes atendidos</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Presencial y online</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-200 rounded-2xl transform rotate-6"
          >
          </div>
          <img
            src="/images/aitana-hero.jpg"
            alt="Aitana Escrivà Conde, psicóloga en Castellón"
            class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-96 object-cover"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
